readable.content: A child is being thrown in the air playfully . A man in an orange jacket playfully tosses a small girl into the air on an empty stretch of beach on an overcast day . A man in an orange vest tossing a child into the air on the beach A man throws a small child up in the air . At a beach , a man in an orange vest tosses a young child into the air .
